long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Replaces the old, boring new tab page with something new!

This extension replaces the "new tab" page with an AI that plays snake! Not only that, but this extension will also give your new tab page a new sleek and clean design, without interfering with  other pages!

Now with a new redesign! The extension has been completely rebuild from the ground up in order to provide a better experience for users.

FEATURES

- Ability to change snake color
- Ability to switch between 4 different search engines
- Favorites/Shortcuts
- Settings kept on browser restart

COMING SOON

- Custom Search Engines


Source Code is available at: https://github.com/Whitelisted1/New-Tab-Snake-AI

Created by: Whitelisted
Snake AI by: Code Bullet (https://thebigcb.com)
